Lindan, Appellant, v. Royal Ins. Co., Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 29, 1889.) Motion to dismiss for failure to serve papers on appeal.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Bartlett, J.

M. J. Stern, for appellant. Shipman, Barlow, larocque & Choate, for respondent.

No opinion. Motion denied.
